msgid ""
"Instead, create a \"price range\" by custom taxonomy, register terms such "
"as \"$0 to $99\", \"$100 to $499\", and \"$500 to $999\", and search for "
"them. Since the server load is lighter, please consider that method as much "
"as possible."
